---
layout: layouts/home.njk
title: 小说书架
---

<section class="books-gallery">
  <h1>📚 书架</h1>
  <p>欢迎来到我的小说书架，这里收藏着我的作品。</p>

  <div class="books-grid">
  {% for book in collections.books %}
    <article class="book-card">
      <a href="/books/{{ book.name }}/">
        <div class="book-cover">
          {% if book.cover %}
          <img src="{{ book.cover }}" alt="{{ book.name }}" loading="lazy" width="150">
          {% else %}
          <div class="book-cover-placeholder">{{ book.name }}</div>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        <h2>{{ book.name }}</h2>
        <p class="chapter-count">{{ book.chapters | length }} 章</p>
      </a>
    </article>
  {% else %}
    <p>书架空空如也，敬请期待...</p>
  {% endfor %}
  </div>
</section>